high_descs: Turn around and head straight until reaching the large gray dining table on the right.
Pick up the mango from the dining table.
Turn back towards the wall you just walked along, walk back the way you came approaching the small coffee table in the corner.
Place the mango down on the coffee table.
anns.task_desc: Move a mango from a dining table to a coffee table.

high_descs: Turn back and walk across the tv, turn right and walk, head to the dining table.
Pick up the mango beside the salt shaker from the dining table.
Turn back and walk, turn left and walk across the tv and head to the coffee table.
Put the mango in the left corner of the coffee table beside to the kettle.
anns.task_desc: Put a mango on the coffee table.

high_descs: Turn around and walk to the dining table to your left
Pick up mango from the dining table
Head towards the door, then hang a left and go to the coffee table.
Place mango on the coffee table
anns.task_desc: Shifting Mango from one place to another
